title: Call of duty 4 100% Acount [Lvl.55] {With Readme file}
description:
Hi, here is a 100% COD4 lvl 55 account(Profile) 
It have i think all golden weapons :D 
and almost all things are done ;) 
 
 
Whats inside the Readme: 
 
[Dutch]
Start eerst Call of duty 4 multiplayer op
- doe dan Options en selecteer Multiplayer options en dan Enter Key code, voer daar in:
QEE8 - YS8Y - TQS4 - MWS8 - 4EC5 

- en dan Verify
nadit sluit daarna cod4 af
_______________
Ga daarna naar de doel waar je call of duty 4 geinstaleerd heb:
ga dan hier heen: Call Of Duty 4playersprofiles

In de rar zie je twee bestanden staan genaamd:
The-Distor
&
Active

kopier de bestanden naar de map Profiles.
dan ben je klaar, en kun je spelen op m'n acount :D

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

[English]
First start CoD4 multiplayer

- go to Options, -> Multiplayer options, then: Enter key code, write there the keycode:

QEE8 - YS8Y - TQS4 - MWS8 - 4EC5 

and do Verify

and close CoD4
_________________
Now go to the location where you installed call of duty 4
than go to: Call Of Duty 4playersprofiles

In the rar you see 1 note and 1 map
copy that to the map Profiles, than your done and you can play on my acount, enjoy!
 
 
I hope you will like it, So enjoy and dont forget to..........
